OL,3,CWarning after batteries cause large
OL,4,Cbin lorry fire in Dorset
OL,6,FDorset Council has warned of the
OL,7,Fdangers of placing batteries in
OL,8,Frecycling bins after a large bin lorry
OL,9,Ffire in Lyme Regis
OL,11,FThe council's waste collection crew
OL,12,Fwere on Summerhill Road when they
OL,13,Fnoticed smoke coming from the back of
OL,14,Fthe truck - originating from batteries
OL,15,Fand a battery-powered drill placed in
OL,16,Fa recycling bin.
