OL,3,CWarning after batteries cause large
OL,4,Cbin lorry fire in Dorset
OL,6,FThe driver of the truck drove away
OL,7,Ffrom nearby cars and ejected the bins
OL,8,Fwhich then burst into flames. The crew
OL,9,Fescaped the incident uninjured and the
OL,10,Fvehicle did not sustain any
OL,11,Fsignificant damage.
OL,13,FA statement by the council's waste
OL,14,Fservices said: "BATTERIES OF ANY KIND
OL,15,FSHOULD NEVER BE PLACED IN ANY
OL,16,FRECYCLING BIN.
OL,18,F"Our crews do not manually sort
OL,19,Fthrough the contents of any bins
OL,20,Fbefore the contents are crushed in the
OL,21,Fback of our collection vehicles.
